STATE EX REL. ARMATAS
v.
DISCIPLINARY COUNSEL 2018-1167 Supreme Court of Ohio. December 19, 2018

O'CONNOR, C.J., and O'DONNELL, KENNEDY, FRENCH, FISCHER, DEWINE, and DEGENARO, JJ., concur.

MERIT DECISION WITHOUT OPINION

On relator's amended motion for leave to file amended complaint. Motion granted. Respondents' motion to dismiss granted. Cause dismissed.
